  <brief_title>Effect of Coadministration of Ume Paste (Prunus Mume) and Ginger Powder</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized, Double-blind, Placebo Controlled, Parallel Group Study to Determine the Effect of Ume Paste and Ginger Powder in Prediabetic Subjects.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
